Modification based on Reduced BNN:

Reduce FC layer; (1024-1024-10 to 128-10)
Delete all bias; (for both FC and CONV layers)

change activation:
from tanh to sigmoid

Performance on cifar-10 Testing dataset:
Error rate:

12.28% (1228 of 10000) 			----binary values 0 and +1
original BNN: about 11.5%		----values +1, -1 and 0
original reducedBNN: about 11.99%	----values +1, -1 and 0

parameter size: about 5.9M bits

